						               													<description>Karchis is in addition to Pachisi. Karchis includes funny cards to add more action, fun and interaction to the game.&amp;#10;Bombs, traps and tricks will appear in the game!&amp;#10;Discover a new meaning for Pachisi!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player starts with 4 cards in his hand. During a turn, you draw a card at the beginning of turn, roll the die and then usually be discarded cards.&amp;#10;Depending on the card, you can play at one time or another. There are cards to change the roll, cards to put traps in boxes, cards to hinder other players, ... There are a variety.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner will be the player to go with one of his chips to the goal box. There are also many more varieties of game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Some sample letters are:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Daltonism: The player moves a pawn of another color.&amp;#10;Dyslexia: the player moves in the opposite direction&amp;#10;Conga: the player moves all his chips at once.&amp;#10;Bomb: a bomb placed in the box where it is placed and roll a dice. The result will be the number of boxes to move each turn until you find a pawn. Then exploded and killed all pawns around.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game incluye:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;120 cards&amp;#10;4 Bomb Marker&amp;#10;4 Trap Marker&amp;#10;Rule Book&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
